          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1724716438675-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1724716438675-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Once the chicken is ready, transfer it to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Return the the<strong> pulled chicken </strong>to the pan with the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>cheesy chicken mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1724716444911-x200.jpg",
