          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1724716450146-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fold each <strong>filled</strong> <strong>tortilla </strong>over so you're left with 3<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>half moon-shaped sandwiches per person and add to a baking tray (or 2!)</p><p>Place another baking tray on top of the filled tortillas to weigh them down</p><p>Put the stacked baking trays in the oven and cook for 15 min or until the tortillas are slightly browned – these are your<strong> smoky chicken quesadillas</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1724716457411-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1724716457411-x400.jpg",
